title: Ubisoft | Welcome to the official Ubisoft websiteArrow LeftArrow Right
description: Welcome to the official website for Ubisoft, creator of Assassin's Creed, Just Dance, Tom Clancy's video game series, Rayman, Far Cry, Watch Dogs and many others. Learn more about our breathtaking games here!
paragraphs: From October 16 to November 6, Doktor’s Curse returns for its fifth terrifying night. In the darkness of Doktor’s Castle, hunters track down fearsome monsters, but this time, the creatures won’t be the only ones hiding in the shadows. Prepare to face your worst nightmares in this sinister game of hide-and-seek!
Unlock access to new rewards and dive right into the action.
PRE-ORDER AND GET BONUS QUEST “THROWN TO THE DOGS”
All your games, friends, and benefits in one place. PC | Console | Mobile
